workouts.name: Morning Yoga
workouts.desc: Enhance your flexibility and balance with this calming yoga session. Flow through a series of poses designed to stretch and strengthen your entire body while promoting relaxation.

workouts.name: HIIT Cardio
workouts.desc: Boost your heart rate with this high-intensity interval training session. Perfect for burning calories and improving cardiovascular health.

workouts.name: Strength Training
workouts.desc: Build muscle and increase your strength with this weight training session. Focus on compound movements for a full-body workout.

workouts.name: Pilates
workouts.desc: Improve your core strength and flexibility with Pilates exercises. This session emphasizes controlled movements and breathing.

workouts.name: Cycling
workouts.desc: Cycle your way to fitness with this intense indoor cycling session. Great for burning calories and building lower body strength.

workouts.name: Swimming
workouts.desc: Dive into this low-impact workout to enhance your cardiovascular fitness and muscle endurance.

workouts.name: Zumba
workouts.desc: Dance your way to fitness with this energetic Zumba session. Perfect for those who enjoy combining fitness with fun.

workouts.name: Running
workouts.desc: Hit the track for this running session designed to boost your endurance and speed. Suitable for all levels.
